  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Creator is a profession that uses items to fight. By killing monsters and dropping items, collecting items, creating items, building your own territory, and defending against monster sieges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the trap-ejection board can set the ejection direction and distance through two boards to relay ejection to kill monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the mechanism-flywheel can launch a flywheel back and forth 8 meters in front of itself, and will damage and bleed the monsters that collide during the flight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the mechanism-ejection ball can perform up to 5 relay ejection damage to monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the power grid tower can form a lightning array with other power grid towers to use thunder balls to attack the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the flying sword tower can shuttle like a swimming fish and kill the enemy quickly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Creator is a profession that uses items to fight. By killing monsters and dropping items, collecting items, creating items, building your own territory, and defending against monster sieges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the trap-ejection board can set the ejection direction and distance through two boards to relay ejection to kill monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the mechanism-flywheel can launch a flywheel back and forth 8 meters in front of itself, and will damage and bleed the monsters that collide during the flight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the mechanism-ejection ball can perform up to 5 relay ejection damage to monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the power grid tower can form a lightning array with other power grid towers to use thunder balls to attack the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.poster.avif?t=1772783598\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.webm?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.mp4?t=1772783598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example, the flying sword tower can shuttle like a swimming fish and kill the enemy quickly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
